{"data":[{"name":"113:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）言え。「私は黎明¹の主*に、ご加護を乞う。","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「黎明（ファラク）」は、「裂く」という語から派生したものとされる。そこから、「（夜の闇から裂き出される）黎明（家畜章９６も参照）」だけでなく、動物、種子、水など、裂かれて出現する全てのものを指す、といった説もある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：２５５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"かれが創造された物の悪から。","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"また、深まった闇（夜）の悪から。","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"また、繋ぎ目に息を吹き込む女たちの悪から。¹","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは魔術師の女たちのこと。魔術を行う際には、紐（ひも）のつなぎ目に息を吹き込んでいたとされる。また、魔術師として特に女性が言及されていることに関しては、「そもそも魔術師が女性なのではなく、『心』という省略された女性名詞にかかっているため」「預言者*ムハンマド*に魔術をかけたユダヤ教徒*ラビード・ブン・アル＝アァサムの娘たちのことを、特に指しているため」（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：７０４－７０５参照）「アラブ人の魔術師の多くは、女性だったため」（イブン・アーシュール３０：６２８参照）といった説がある。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2150],[3,2150,4440],[4,4440,4630],[5,4630,5935]]}},{"name":"113:5","price":"また、嫉妬¹した妬み屋の悪から」。","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6230,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「嫉妬（ハサド） 」とは、恩恵を授かった誰かから、その恩恵が消え去ってしまうことを望むこと（ムヤッサル６０４頁参照）。筆章５１訳注内の「アイン」についての説明も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ḥāsidin idhā ḥasada ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) an envier","when","he envies","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ḥāsidin","idhā","ḥasada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1990],[3,1990,3160],[4,3160,3750],[5,3750,5605]]}},{"name":"114:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）言え。「私は人々の主*に、ご加護を乞う、","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"人々の王、","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"（真に崇拝*されるべき唯一の存在である、）人々の神¹に、","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「神」については、雌牛章１３３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"頻りに身を潜ませて囁きかける者¹（シャイターン*）の悪から。","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　シャイターン*は不注意な時には囁きかけてくるが、アッラー*が想起されると「身を潜めてしまう」（ムヤッサル６０４頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"（それは、）人々の胸に（悪を）囁きかける、","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"ジン*と人々である」。¹","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　家畜章１１２も参照。尚、人間のシャイターン*の「囁き」とは、同情的な忠告者を装（よそお）って、ジン*のシャイターン*が囁くようなことを、忠告の形で胸に訴（うった）え かけること（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：７０８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}}],"dua":{"id":4,"name":"Dua for Protection","arabicName":"دعاء الحماية","reference":"113:1-5, 114:1-6","verseTitle":"The Protection and Refuge Supplication","significanceReason":"Powerful duas seeking protection from negative energies, evil intentions, and spiritual harm. Considered a shield against potential dangers."},"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}